tool_description: This API helps to query for transfer news, latest or record transfers, rumors, player market value, etc... to create a sporting site/application such as transfermarkt.com
name: TransferMarket
title: TransferMarket

api_list.name: transfers/list-rumors
api_list.description: List transfer rumors along with players info, and estimated market value

required_parameters.name: competitionIds
required_parameters.description: The value of id field returned in .../search or .../competitions/list... endpoints. DO NOT use together with clubIds and  playerIds parameters. Separated by coma for multiple values. Ex : IT1,GB1,etc...

optional_parameters.name: positionId
optional_parameters.description: One of the following 1-Goalkeeper|2-Sweeper|3-Centre-Back|4-Left-Back|5-Right-Back|6-Defensive Midfield|7-Central Midfield|8-Right Midfield|9-Left Midfield|10-Attacking Midfield|11-Left Winger|12-Right Winger|13-Second Striker|14-Centre-Forward

optional_parameters.name: playerIds
optional_parameters.description: The value of id field returned in .../search or .../clubs/get-squad or .../transfers/list... endpoints. DO NOT use together with clubIds and competitionIds parameter. Separated by coma for multiple values. Ex : 68778,405686,etc...

optional_parameters.name: clubIds
optional_parameters.description: The value of id field returned in .../search or .../clubs/list-by-competition endpoints. DO NOT use together with competitionIds and playerIds parameters. Separated by coma for multiple values. Ex : 631,383,985,27,etc...

optional_parameters.name: minValue
optional_parameters.description: The min market value of players. Ex : 9000000

optional_parameters.name: maxValue
optional_parameters.description: The max market value of players. Ex : 151000000
